  <lb/>As to Billy's adieu to the ship <hi rend="italic"><hi rend="underline">Rights</hi>- <metamark facs="#img_499-0019" rend="#HM _HMp" place="below" function="folio" change="#StGa">17</metamark>
  <lb/>-<hi rend="underline">of</hi>-<hi rend="underline">Man</hi></hi>, which the boarding
<lb/>lieutenant had indeed reported to <add facs="#img_499-0002" rend="no-caret _ink1" place="inline" hand="#HM" change="#StGa">him</add>
<lb/><del facs="#img_499-0003" rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#HM" change="#StGa">the Captain</del>, but<add facs="#img_499-0017" rend="no-caret _HMp" place="inline" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">,</add> <add facs="#img_499-0004" rend="no-caret _HMp" place="above" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">in a deferential way</add> more as a good story
<lb/>than aught else, <add facs="#img_499-0016" rend="no-caret _ink2" place="above" hand="#HM" change="#StGa">Captain Vere</add><del facs="#img_499-0009" rend="multi-stroke _ink1" hand="#HM" change="#StGa">he</del><add facs="#img_499-0021" rend="no-caret _ink1" place="inline" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">,</add> <metamark facs="#img_499-0005" rend="#HM _ink1" place="inline" function="insertion-device" change="#StBc">^</metamark> <add facs="#img_499-0006" rend="insertion-device _ink1" place="above" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">tho mistakenly understanding it <add facs="#img_499-0020" rend="bubble _ink1" place="inline" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">as a satiric sally,</add></add> had but thought
<lb/>so much the better of <metamark facs="#img_499-0007" rend="#HM _ink1" place="inline" function="caret" change="#StBc">^</metamark> <add facs="#img_499-0008" rend="caret" place="above" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">the impressed man</add> <del facs="#img_499-0010" rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">Billy</del> for it;
<lb/>as a military <subst facs="#img_499-0018"><del facs="#img_499-0018" rend="overwritten _HMp" type="superimposed" hand="#HM"><app><rdg resp="#HS">sailor's</rdg></app></del><add facs="#img_499-0018" rend="superimposed _ink1" type="superimposed" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">sailor</add></subst>, admiring the
<lb/>spirit that could take an <del facs="#img_499-0011" rend="single-stroke _ink1" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">ab</del> arbitrary
<lb/>enlistment so <subst><del facs="#img_499-0015" rend="superimposed" type="overwritten" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">merryly</del> <add facs="#img_499-0015" rend="overwritten" type="overwritten" place="inline" hand="#HM" change="#StBc">merrily</add></subst> <del facs="#img_499-0013" rend="erasure" hand="#HM" change="#StBc"><add facs="#img_499-0013" rend="no-caret _HMp" place="below" hand="#HM" change="#StBc"><app><rdg resp="#HS">wittily</rdg></app></add></del> and sensibly.
